---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bespoke & Refresher — TT Motorcycle School"
  description="Bespoke and refresher motorcycle training in Sussex with TT Motorcycle School. Returning to riding, or need to brush up on specific skills? We can help."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">Tailored to You</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Bespoke &amp; Refresher Training</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        Had a break from riding? Want to work on something specific? Our bespoke
        and refresher sessions are designed around your individual needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Gearing Up for Gears</h2>
        <p>
          Been riding an automatic on your CBT and ready to master a geared
          motorcycle? We run dedicated hour-long sessions to teach you how to
          ride a manual geared bike with confidence. Sessions run at weekends -
          check out bespoke prices <a href="/prices/">here</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          You will need to bring your CBT certificate and driving licence to
          attend.
          <a href="tel:01273041925">Call us to book</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ideal for 17-year-olds who have been riding the 50cc scooter since
          they were 16 and are now ready to step up!
        </p>

        <h2>Hourly Lessons</h2>
        <p>
          Got your CBT but can't commit to an intensive course or a full day of
          training? We deliver hourly lessons — as many as you like — on either
          your own bike or one of ours, at times to suit you. The perfect option
          if you can't take that day off work.
        </p>

        <h2>Refresher Sessions</h2>
        <p>
          Have a licence and a bike but not quite got the confidence to get out
          there? Or perhaps you simply haven't been in the saddle for some time
          and you've got your eye on that Harley, V-Max or GSX-R?
        </p>
        <p>
          Take some refresher sessions with us to regain your control and
          confidence and get back to riding the way you want to.
        </p>

        <h2>Bespoke Sessions</h2>
        <p>
          Not sure exactly what you need? Tell us your goals and we'll design a
          session around them. Popular requests include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Motorway riding confidence</li>
          <li>Rural road and country lane technique</li>
          <li>Slow-speed manoeuvres (car parks, tight spaces)</li>
          <li>Night riding preparation</li>
          <li>Riding a new or unfamiliar type of motorcycle</li>
          <li>Pre-long trip confidence building</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
          <CTAButton
            href="/contact/"
            label="Get in Touch"
            variant="accent"
            size="md"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar__card sidebar__card--plain">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Related</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar__links">
            <li><a href="/OneToOneTraining/">One-to-One Training</a></li>
            <li><a href="/advanced-rider/">Advanced Rider</a></li>
            <li><a href="/prices/">Pricing</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    }
  }

  .sidebar__card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .sidebar__card--plain {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .sidebar__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .sidebar__links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .sidebar__links a {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .sidebar__links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
